title: LeBron James, Anthony Davis, Tom Brady, & Dak Prescott
itunes:title: LeBron James, Anthony Davis, Tom Brady, & Dak Prescott
description:
Colin defends LeBron James, gives his thoughts on Anthony Davis criticism, why he feels Tom Brady will go back to the Patriots, and why Dak Prescott will get the contract he wants. Guests include Ric Bucher, Rob Ryan, Sarah Kustok, Frank Clark, and Antonio Cromartie.
